    {{ include('/public/static/components/support-section.html.twig', {class: 'vika-alex'}) }}

    <section class="compare-questions">
        <div class="container">
            <header class="compare-questions__header">
                <h2 class="compare-questions__header-title title title--h2">{{ 'Appointment Scheduling Software FAQs'|trans }}</h2>
            </header>
            <div class="accordion-list">
                <script type="application/ld+json">
                    {
                        "@context": "https://schema.org",
                        "@type": "FAQPage",
                        "mainEntity": [
                            {
                                "@type": "Question",
                                "name": "What is online scheduling?",
                                "acceptedAnswer": {
                                    "@type": "Answer",
                                    "text": "By implementing online scheduling, you allow your clients to book your services from your website or social media profiles whenever it suits them. So instead of having to answer phone calls or emails for booking requests, you save some time for yourself and your clients. On top of that, you make your business available 24/7 as clients just have to find you online and book from there."
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "@type": "Question",
                                "name": "What are the key benefits of an online booking system?",
                                "acceptedAnswer": {
                                    "@type": "Answer",
                                    "text": "The main benefit is saving you and your clients endless time trying to organise bookings. On top of that, you will reduce no shows as the booking system will send out automatic confirmations and reminders. Other advantages are asking questions upon booking, accepting deposits or full payment upon booking, offering coupons to get more business, sending come back soon reminders, and more. "
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "@type": "Question",
                                "name": "How can I attract new customers with a booking system?",
                                "acceptedAnswer": {
                                    "@type": "Answer",
                                    "text": "You can run a social media campaign with a direct link to your booking website, make sure all your social media profiles include a booking link, add your business to Google business, add a booking link there, and more."
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "@type": "Question",
                                "name": "What is an appointment reminder system?",
                                "acceptedAnswer": {
                                    "@type": "Answer",
                                    "text": "Most scheduling solutions include appointment reminders. Appointment reminders enable businesses to automatically send notifications to clients about an upcoming appointment or event. Typically, appointment reminders are sent to customers via email or SMS messages, and they have proven to reduce no-shows considerably!"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "@type": "Question",
                                "name": "How to accept bookings on Facebook and Instagram?",
                                "acceptedAnswer": {
                                    "@type": "Answer",
                                    "text": "By using a scheduling solution that has natively integrated with Facebook, you can add a \"Book now\" button to your Facebook and Instagram profiles which can help you to turn leads into customers more quickly."
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "@type": "Question",
                                "name": "What is the best scheduling app?",
                                "acceptedAnswer": {
                                    "@type": "Answer",
                                    "text": "That really depends on your needs. There are multiple scheduling apps on the market, and there is no one solution that is best for every business. You need to know what you want to achieve by implementing a booking system."
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "@type": "Question",
                                "name": "What is the best scheduling app for small businesses?",
                                "acceptedAnswer": {
                                    "@type": "Answer",
                                    "text": "What you need to do first is to figure out what you want to achieve. Do you only want a tool to schedule your meetings or do you also want to accept payments, offer different locations, sell products, offer coupons and gift cards and so on? After you have defined your needs then you can start to find the best solutions."
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "@type": "Question",
                                "name": "How do you create a booking system?",
                                "acceptedAnswer": {
                                    "@type": "Answer",
                                    "text": "That's easy - you just sign up for SimplyBook.me and you will get a booking website where your clients can book an appointment with you. If you already have a website then you can just add a booking widget to your website, provided by SimplyBook.me. If you need any help with setting up the specifics, contact our Live Chat and get an immediate answer 24h during the working week."
                                }
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                </script>

                <article class="accordion-card">
                    <div class="accordion-title">{{ 'What is online scheduling?'|trans }}</div>
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p class="p">{{ 'By implementing online scheduling, you allow your clients to book your services from your website or social media profiles whenever it suits them.  So instead of having to answer phone calls or emails for booking requests, you save some time for yourself and your clients. On top of that, you make your business available 24/7 as clients just have to find you online and book from there.'|trans }}</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="accordion-card">
                    <div class="accordion-title">{{ 'What are the key benefits of an online booking system?'|trans }}</div>
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p class="p">{{ 'The main benefit is saving you and your clients endless time trying to organise bookings. On top of that, you will reduce no shows as the booking system will send out automatic confirmations and reminders.  Other advantages are asking questions upon booking, accepting deposits or full payment upon booking, offering coupons to get more business, sending come back soon reminders, and more. If you are not convinced, <a href="%link%">take a look</a>! '|trans|replace({'%link%': path('benefits_scheduling_software_page')})|raw() }}</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="accordion-card">
                    <div class="accordion-title">{{ 'How can I attract new customers with a booking system?'|trans }}</div>
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p class="p">{{ 'You can run a social media campaign with a direct link to your booking website, make sure all your social media profiles include a booking link, add your business to Google business, add a booking link there, and more.  Read more <a href="%link%">here</a> about 9 tips to get more bookings.'|trans|replace({'%link%': 'https://news.simplybook.me/9-ways-to-get-more-bookings-on-your-business-website/'})|raw() }}</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="accordion-card">
                    <div class="accordion-title">{{ 'What is an appointment reminder system?'|trans }}</div>
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p class="p">{{ 'Most scheduling solutions include appointment reminders. Appointment reminders enable businesses to automatically send notifications to clients about an upcoming appointment or event. Typically, appointment reminders are sent to customers via email or SMS messages, and they have proven to reduce no-shows considerably!'|trans }}</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="accordion-card">
                    <div class="accordion-title">{{ 'How to accept bookings on Facebook and Instagram?'|trans }}</div>
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p class="p">{{ 'By using a scheduling solution that has natively integrated with Facebook, you can add a "Book now" button to your Facebook and Instagram profiles which can help you to turn leads into customers more quickly. <a href="%link%">Here</a> is a list of scheduling platforms that offer Facebook and Instagram bookings.'|trans|replace({'%link%': 'https://www.getapp.com/operations-management-software/scheduling/w/facebook/'})|raw() }}</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="accordion-card">
                    <div class="accordion-title">{{ 'What is the best scheduling app?'|trans }}</div>
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p class="p">{{ 'That really depends on your needs.  There are multiple scheduling apps on the market, and there is no one solution that is best for every business. You need to know what you want to achieve by implementing a booking system. Here come a few that are known to be outstanding for different needs:'|trans }}</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>{{ 'SimplyBook.me - Very flexible with beautiful customisable booking website, offers payments, coupons, gift cards, memberships and more'|trans }}</li>
                            <li>{{ 'SimplyMeet.me - if you only need to schedule meetings and integrate with other calendars and video platforms'|trans }}</li>
                            <li>{{ 'HouseCallPro - For home services including estimates and more specifically designed for this industry'|trans }}</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="accordion-card">
                    <div class="accordion-title">{{ 'What is the best scheduling app for small businesses?'|trans }}</div>
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p class="p">{{ 'What you need to do first is to figure out what you want to achieve. Do you only want a tool to schedule your meetings or do you also want to accept payments, offer different locations, sell products, offer coupons and gift cards and so on?  After you have defined your needs then you can start to find the best solutions.  SimplyBook.me and SimplyMeet.me are two different online booking tools which cater to different needs, if you want to know more, click <a href="%link%">here</a>.'|trans|replace({'%link%' : path('sb_vs_sm_landing')})|raw() }}</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="accordion-card">
                    <div class="accordion-title">{{ 'How do you create a booking system?'|trans }}</div>
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p class="p">{{ 'That\'s easy - you just sign up for SimplyBook.me and you will get a booking website where your clients can book an appointment with you.  If you already have a website then you can just add a booking widget to your website, provided by SimplyBook.me.  If you need any help with setting up the specifics, contact our Live Chat and get an immediate answer 24h during the working week.'|trans }}</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

{% endif %}
